			if (otherPIndex != -1) {
				client p = (client)server.playerHandler.players[otherPIndex];
				p.playermember = 1;
				p.sM(c.playerName + " has made you an Member!");
				c.sM("You have made " + p.playerName + " an Mamber!!");
				p.disconnected = true;
				p.logoutButton = true;
			} else {
				c.sM("The name doesnt exist.");
			}
		} catch (Exception e) {
			c.sM("Try entering a name you want to make a member");
		}
	}[/quote]
